FARLOOK

Usage       : cast 'farlook' <victim>
Accumulative: -
Duration    : Instantaneous

   This spell is used to look at the room of a certain person or mob.  It
essentially takes a snapshot at the time of casting and makes it visible
to all those in the room at the time.

ex. cast 'farlook' JoeBlow(This will look at the room that JoeBlow is in.)

